      "title": "Bandula Gunawardena resigns as Minister and Pohottuvu",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Transport Minister Bandula Gunawardena has decided to resign from his ministry. He has also decided to resign from the party membership of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna."
      ],
